   <conbody>
      <p class="- topic/p ">There are multiple customer service offers that can be ordered
when required. The following sections gives an overview of the different
services.</p>
      <section class="- topic/section ">
         <title class="- topic/title ">Customer Training</title>
         <p class="- topic/p ">For more information about
potential training offers please contact your local sales representative.</p>
      </section>
      <section class="- topic/section ">
         <title class="- topic/title ">Installation Supervision and Start-Up</title>
         <sectiondiv class="- topic/sectiondiv ">
            <p class="- topic/p ">Service engineer(s) supervise the installation process and performs
the start-up of the systems on site.</p>
            <p class="- topic/p ">The supervision includes
the follow inspections:<ul class="- topic/ul ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">Visual inspection of location and environment for the system
and battery</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">Wiring and cabinet installation check</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">Power module installation check</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">Visual and safety check for battery</p>
                  </li>
               </ul>
            </p>
         </sectiondiv>
         <sectiondiv class="- topic/sectiondiv ">
            <p class="- topic/p ">The start-up process also includes:<ul class="- topic/ul ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">Firmware updates</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">Function and system tests</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">Measurements check on the front panel</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">Basic operation information</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">Completion of site acceptance test (SAT) report</p>
                  </li>
               </ul>
            </p>
         </sectiondiv>
      </section>
      <section class="- topic/section ">
         <title class="- topic/title ">Preventive Maintenance</title>
         <sectiondiv class="- topic/sectiondiv ">
            <ul class="- topic/ul ">
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">Yearly preventive maintenance</p>
               </li>
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">8-10 years preventive maintenance, parts replacement</p>
               </li>
            </ul>
         </sectiondiv>
      </section>
      <section class="- topic/section ">
         <title class="- topic/title ">Corrective Maintenance</title>
         <sectiondiv class="- topic/sectiondiv ">
            <p class="- topic/p ">Our service
engineers are available to assist on-site in the event that technical
repairs or part replacement services are needed.</p>
         </sectiondiv>
      </section>
      <section class="- topic/section ">
         <title class="- topic/title ">Spare Parts</title>
         <sectiondiv class="- topic/sectiondiv ">
            <ul class="- topic/ul ">
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">Spare parts used during start-up</p>
               </li>
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">Spare parts used during preventive maintenance</p>
               </li>
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">Strategical and critical spare parts to have on stock</p>
               </li>
            </ul>
         </sectiondiv>
      </section>
      <section class="- topic/section ">
         <title class="- topic/title ">Updates, Upgrades and Modifications</title>
         <sectiondiv class="- topic/sectiondiv ">
            <p class="- topic/p ">Software and firmware updates to the latest revision with the
latest functions.</p>
            <p class="- topic/p ">During a systemâ€™s lifespan customer
needs might change and modifications might be necessary. Optional
features may be added to existing systems, for example a Reality battery
management system (G.BMS) or additional communication devices or expansion
ADBUS cards.</p>
         </sectiondiv>
      </section>
      <section class="- topic/section ">
         <title class="- topic/title ">Digital Services</title>
         <sectiondiv class="- topic/sectiondiv ">
            <p class="- topic/p ">Monitor and
manage critical assets on site or remotely with high cyber security
can increase efficiency. It can help to efficiently operate selected
systems and reduce operation costs with flexible service plans.</p>
         </sectiondiv>
      </section>
      <section class="- topic/section ">
         <title class="- topic/title ">Battery Replacement</title>
         <sectiondiv class="- topic/sectiondiv ">
            <p class="- topic/p ">The lifetime
of batteries varies between 4 and 20 years depending on the type of
battery, environmental conditions and maintenance.</p>
            <p class="- topic/p ">Even with
proper maintenance batteries will have to be replaced at some time.
Reality provides service offers for preventive maintenance and replacement
of batteries.</p>
         </sectiondiv>
      </section>
      <section class="- topic/section ">
         <title class="- topic/title ">Retrofit or Replace</title>
         <sectiondiv class="- topic/sectiondiv ">
            <p class="- topic/p ">
               <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Retrofit: </b> Replace an existing system with the same design and dimensions as
the existing system.</p>
            <p class="- topic/p ">
               <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Replace: </b> Replace an existing system
with a new design meeting the latest industry requirement.</p>
         </sectiondiv>
      </section>
      <section class="- topic/section ">
         <title class="- topic/title ">Site Audit</title>
         <sectiondiv class="- topic/sectiondiv ">
            <p class="- topic/p ">Reality system have
a designed lifetime of 20 years, during this time your site might
grow or change. Reality can assist with a detailed on-site check to: <ul class="- topic/ul ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">Prepare for future service recommendations</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">Discuss retrofit or replacement for systems nearing expected
end of life</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">Organize installed base</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">Review of the site environment for external factors that can
affect the system</p>
                  </li>
               </ul>
            </p>
         </sectiondiv>
      </section>
